summary: Harry lending the missus his clothes and the fans going crazy over it
question: Harry lending the missus his clothes and the fans going crazy over it
answer:
it would happen twice as often when missus needs new clothes because of her bump.

missus wearing the harley davidson shirt, the styles shirt, the shirt he wore on carpool karaoke, and even his suit jackets and glittery shirts?

the fans would go crazy because the missus just looks down-right adorable in their idol’s clothes and he looks even happier when he’s looking at her wearing something of his.

he wouldn’t even just lend the clothes, he’d give it to the missus because it looks better on her and his bub (he included baby angel because she’s part of the look and part of them) and he’d be constantly rummaging his closet to find things for the missus.

and guess what harry does next:

“love? you uhm, you have a fitting tomorrow. we have a fitting tomorrow. we’re gonna get some matching clothes from harris and from gucci.”
